Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:26.41,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{He slept through that racket?}Ồn vậy mà vẫn ngủ được à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:30.00,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Hey, the warning bell's ringing.}Nè, chuông rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:36.79,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Oh, you the transfer student who did \Nthat speech at the opening ceremony?}À, cậu là học sinh chuyển \Ntrường phát biểu ở lễ nhập học.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:38.58,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Yes, that's me.}À ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:43.04,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I'm Alisa Mikhailovna Kujo. Nice to meet you.}Tôi là Alisa Mikhailovna Kujo. Rất vui được gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:46.17,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Hi. I'm Kuze Masachika.}Masachika Kuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.48,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Nice to meet you too...}Rất vui được gặp...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:50.78,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Oh?}Ô?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:53.33,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Heya, Hikaru. Didn't know \Nyou were in this class.}Hikaru, cậu ở đây lúc nào thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:54.67,flashback,HIKARU,0,0,0,,{I am.}Từ đầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.67,flashback,HIKARU,0,0,0,,{Takeshi's here too, by the way.}Takeshi cũng ở đây nữa đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.23,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{So he is.}Thật kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.23,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord3\fs25\c&H5C6263&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(314.143,129.143)}{Science}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:04.23,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Crap, I forgot my textbook.}Mình quên sách rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:06.45,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Sorry. Hikaru, Show me yours.}Hikaru, cho tớ xem với.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:07.48,flashback,HIKARU,0,0,0,,{Sure.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:07.86,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord3\fs25\c&H5C6263&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(314.143,129.143)\fade(1,300)}{Science}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:08.74,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord3\fs25\c&H5C6263&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(314.143,129.143)\fade(400,1)}{P.E.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.42,flashback,GIRL3,0,0,0,,{That was rough, huh?}Mệt ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:15.32,flashback,GIRL2,0,0,0,,{I know, right?}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:16.07,flashback italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Wha...}Cái...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.12,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord3\fs25\c&H5C6263&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(314.143,129.143)\fade(1,300)}{P.E.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:18.66,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord3\fs25\c&H5C6263&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(314.143,129.143)\fade(200,1)}{Math}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:25.80,flashback italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I guess slackers are everywhere, \Neven in prestigious schools like this one.}Đúng là ở đâu cũng có kẻ lười biếng nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:36.43,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fnComic Sans Ms\b1\fs25\pos(420.571,350)\frz347.9}{School Festival starts in 14 days!\NHaunted House\NConfirmed!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:37.14,flashback,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{Uh...}Xem nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.70,flashback,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{We're gonna need shutters to make the paths.}Chúng ta cần cái màn để tạo đường đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.85,flashback,HIKARU,0,0,0,,{How are we getting costumes for all the ghosts?}Còn trang phục của mấy con ma?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.94,flashback,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{Wait, wait! One thing at a time!}Khoan khoan! Từ từ từng cái thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:47.46,flashback,BOYF,0,0,0,,{Man, I had no idea it'd be so much work.}Không ngờ lại vất vả đến thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:48.76,flashback,BOYD,0,0,0,,{Same.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:51.95,flashback,GIRL3,0,0,0,,{Not going home yet, Kujo-san?}Cậu vẫn chưa về hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:55.01,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{No, I'll work on this some more.}Ừm, tớ làm thêm chút nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:56.31,flashback,GIRL3,0,0,0,,{Yeah?}Thế hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:57.27,flashback,GIRL3,0,0,0,,{See you, then.}Vậy nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:07:59.72,flashback,GIRL2,0,0,0,,{Are we gonna make it?}Có kịp không nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.33,flashback,GIRL3,0,0,0,,{Who knows? But it's just \Na school festival, anyway.}Ai biết? Cơ mà lễ hội văn hoá thôi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.97,flashback,GIRL3,0,0,0,,Chẳng ai quan tâm đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.80,flashback italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,{It's happening again.}Lại nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.09,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Ouch!}Đau.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:18.44,flashback italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I just want to do the best I can...}Mình chỉ muốn cố hết sức...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:21.60,flashback italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,{and not throw in the towel.}và không muốn từ bỏ thôi mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:24.55,flashback italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,{If that's going to leave me all alone,}Nếu làm vậy sẽ khiến mình lẻ loi,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:28.73,flashback italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,{then fine, whatever.}thì cũng chả sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:35.99,flashback,MUNECHIKA,0,0,0,,{Figured you'd still be here.}Cậu vẫn còn chưa về nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:38.45,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Kuze-kun? What are you doing here?}Kuze? Cậu làm gì ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:41.45,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Hey. Just had a few things to take care of.}Cậu vất vả rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:44.46,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{You should go home, Kujo-san.}Cậu cũng nên về đi Kujo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:48.93,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{We can all get together \Nand handle this stuff tomorrow.}Cái đó để mai mọi người cùng làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.70,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Don't mind me.}Đừng để ý đến tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:53.34,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I'll go home after I get some more done.}Tôi làm thêm chút nữa rồi về.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.34,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Yeah? Well, uh...}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:09:01.58,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{The handicrafts club agreed to \Nhelp us out with the costumes.}CLB thủ công đã đồng ý giúp vụ trang phục rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.30,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:05.10,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Check this out. \NPermission to stay overnight at school.}Còn đây là giấy phép cho ở lại trường qua đêm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:09.61,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{A special event like that will light a fire \Nunder the unmotivated folks, too.}Những sự kiện như này\N sẽ khiến mọi người có động lực nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.36,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{How did you pull that off?}Sao cậu lại có nó?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:16.93,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Asked the former student council \Npresident to pull some strings.}Nhờ cựu hội trưởng giúp đỡ thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:19.99,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{And I told the handicrafts club \Nour boys would help with their work.}Và tớ kêu mấy tên con trai\N lớp mình phụ CLB thủ công rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:24.27,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{If we frame it as a chance \Nto show off to the girls there,}Nếu nói với tụi nó đây là cơ hội để cua gái,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:26.54,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{the boys will gladly go for it.}thì thằng nào cũng lao vào giúp cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:31.50,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{That's the deal, \Nso you should really call it a day.}Tóm lại là hôm nay về đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:34.82,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{There's no point grinding away all on your own.}Cậu cố gắng một mình cũng chẳng được gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:40.26,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{What do you mean, "There's no point"?}Chẳng được gì là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:47.34,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I just want to make this a good attraction \Nif I'm going to be participating in it!}Tôi chỉ muốn biến mọi chuyện trở nên\N thú vị nếu mình tham gia thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:51.16,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I don't want to put out something shoddy!}Tôi không muốn làm nửa mùa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:54.55,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I refuse to compromise on the quality!}Tôi sẽ không bao giờ làm qua loa cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:10:00.74,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord0\fs35\frz343.3\c&H7D8086&\move(296,82.571,392,82.571)}{Haunted}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:59.76,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{But I know that's just my ego talking!}Nhưng tôi biết mình chỉ đang thoả mãn cái tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:04.75,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I get that you all don't care \Nabout it as much as I do!}Dù gì cũng chẳng ai quan tâm tôi nghiêm túc thế nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.75,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{That's why I'm taking on the load \Nand putting in all this effort!}Thế nên tôi sẽ cố gắng hết sức phần của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:10.86,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Am I doing anything wrong?!}Như vậy là sai sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:16.57,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{You're putting effort into the wrong things.}Cậu nỗ lực vào nhầm thứ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:17.54,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:20.97,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{School festival attractions \Naren't meant to be built alone.}Lễ hội văn hoá không phải nơi nỗ lực một mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:24.50,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{The whole point of them is for us all \Nto work together to create something.}Mà là nơi mọi người cùng nhau tạo ra gì đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.64,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{If you wanna make it the best it can be,}Nếu cậu muốn làm nó tốt nhất,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:30.17,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{then you should be focusing on how to \Nmotivate the whole class, don't you think?}thì hãy nghĩ cách thúc đẩy cả lớp đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.42,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:40.15,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Well, I suppose putting it like that \Nwould only piss you off.}Cơ mà nói thế chỉ làm cậu thêm bực mình thôi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.07,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{My bad.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:47.54,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{I get that you're doing \Nwhat you can, and I appreciate it.}Tớ rất cảm kích những gì cậu đã làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:58.51,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I'm leaving.}Tôi về đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:01.08,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Great. Have a good night.}Ờ, cậu vất vả rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:05.59,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{What's with him?}Cậu ta bị gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:06.89,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{What's his problem?!}Vậy là sao chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.14,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{What's his deal...}Cậu ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:24.28,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\b1\an7\fnComic Sans MS\fs25\c&HCED9CA&}{Overnight Session!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:22.07,flashback,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{There you have it!}Thế nên là...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.28,flashback,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{We'll work on the festival stuff}Chúng ta sẽ cùng nhau làm việc
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:28.04,flashback,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and}{\i0}{ have some hide-and-seek and \Ntest-of-courage sessions on school grounds.}vào ban đêm thì chơi trốn tìm và thi can đảm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:32.17,flashback,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{We're gonna have \Na pre-pre-pre-festival party all of our own!}Chúng ta sẽ tổ chức tiệc trước lễ hội!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:36.17,flashback,ALL,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:37.67,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\b1\fnComic Sans Ms\fs25\pos(108.571,198)\frz356.3}{Hustle!\NSchool festival starts\Nin 6 days!}Còn 6 ngày
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:57.15,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an8\b1\c&H605450&\3c&HFDFFFC&}{Seirei Fall Festival}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.66,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnGeorgia\c&H353B44&\an9\3c&HF8F9FA&}{Best Attraction Award\NClass Event Category\NClass 3-B}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:26.68,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Oh, hey, Kujo-san.}A, cậu vất vả rồi Kujo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:30.86,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{This school can be old-fashioned \Nin the weirdest ways.}Ngôi truòng này nhiều khi lỗi thời thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:33.74,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Who still holds a folk dance \Nfor the after-party?}Giờ nào rồi còn tổ chức nhảy dân gian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:37.27,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{May I sit here?}Tôi ngồi cạnh nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.78,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Sure, but aren't you gonna dance?}Ừm, nhưng cậu không nhảy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:43.77,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{I'm sure everyone and their mother \Nwants to dance with you.}Nếu là cậu thì không chỉ mọi người mà \Nmẹ của họ cũng muốn nhảy cùng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:46.60,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Oh, wait. Do you not know \Nhow to folk dance or something?}Hay cậu không biết nhảy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:50.54,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Rude. I practiced ballet as a child, you know.}Này nhé, tôi học múa ba lê từ hồi bé tí rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:54.36,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{This simplistic dance \Nwon't be a problem in the least.}Cái điệu nhảy đơn giản đó thì 1 giây.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:59.67,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{But I turned everyone down saying \NI couldn't dance because I can't be bothered.}Nhưng phiền phức lắm nên tôi từ chối hết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:02.42,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Fighting 'em off must've been a pain.}Cậu vất vả rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:06.00,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Not really. I'm used to it, \Nso it wasn't a big deal.}Không hẳn, tôi quen rồi, cũng chẳng có gì to tát.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:07.66,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{You don't say.}Vậy à...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.70,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{That's our ice princess for you.}Không hổ danh công chúa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:10.68,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{What was that?}Cái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.25,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Wait, you didn't know?}Cậu không biết à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:13.11,flashbacktop,BGBOY,0,0,0,,{May I have this dance with you?}Tớ nhảy với cậu nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:16.06,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{That's what the others \Nhave taken to calling you lately.}Gần đây mọi người hay gọi cậu vậy đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.71,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Hửm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:20.09,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Trông có vẻ không vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:23.06,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Yeah. That's because I'm not.}Có vẻ gì. Tôi không vui thật đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.57,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Why's that? 'Cause they're \Nindirectly calling you a loner?}Tại sao? Vì họ nghĩ cậu là kẻ cô độc hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:30.18,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{That's not it. Can you stop \Nwith that mocking tone?}Không phải. Mà cậu đừng có khịa tôi nữa đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.35,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Sorry.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:35.57,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{The "princess" part is what I take issue with.}Tôi không thích chữ công chúa đó thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:37.33,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Isn't that a compliment?}Tớ nghĩ đó là lời khen mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:42.13,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{It makes it sound like I'm a silver-spoon snob.}Nó khiến tôi như kẻ hợm hĩnh vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:45.76,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{That's one way to look at it.}À thì... cũng đúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:51.22,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Sure, I was born with \Nabove-average looks and talent.}Đúng là tôi sinh ra với tài năng\N lẫn sắc đẹp hơn người.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:56.15,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{But never once have I coasted by on that alone.}Nhưng tôi chưa từng lợi dụng điều đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:14:01.48,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{It annoys me when all my efforts \Nget ignored in favor of my birth.}Thật khó chịu khi những \Nnỗ lực của mình bị xem thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.37,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{That makes sense.}Ra là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:07.36,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{I'll make sure not to call you that, then.}Vậy thì tớ sẽ không gọi cậu như vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:09.11,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Yeah?}Vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.89,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Kuze-kun.}Cảm ơn Kuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:14.12,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Hmm? For what?}Vì điều gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.56,flashbacktop,BGGIRL,0,0,0,,{Can you even dance?}Cậu có nhảy được không đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:18.27,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{You were right. I was wrong.}Cậu nói phải, tôi đã sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:20.60,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{If I'd tried to do it all alone,}Nếu làm điều này một mình,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:24.81,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I would've never gotten to experience \Nthe school festival this way.}thì tôi đã chẳng thể tận hưởng lễ hội văn hoá.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:30.34,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Also, I'm sorry for \Nlashing out at you the other day.}Và xin lỗi vì cáu gắt với cậu hôm trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.27,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Don't let it bother you.}Không có gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:34.50,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{All I did was file some paperwork.}Tớ chỉ làm vài việc giấy tờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:38.31,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{I didn't put in half the work \Nyou or Takeshi did.}Còn lại hầu như cậu với Takeshi làm cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.61,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{But it does bother me.}Nhưng tôi không nghĩ thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:42.61,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I want to apologize for that}Tôi muốn xin lỗi cậu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:46.84,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{and repay you for all this in a tangible way.}và làm gì đó xem như trả ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:48.95,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Is there anything you want?}Có gì cậu muốn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:51.01,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{"Repay me," eh?}Trả ơn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:53.40,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{You're not allowed to refuse.}Không được từ chối nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:55.00,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Hmm...}Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.45,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Wait, I got it!}A, phải rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:15:01.96,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Isn't there a Russian custom where people\N call each other by special nicknames?}Người Nga có phong tục gọi nhau bằng biệt danh nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.77,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Diminutives? What about them?}Tại sao tự nhiên lại...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:06.98,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Alisha? Or would it be Aliska?}Alisha? Aliska?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:10.09,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Alya. That's what my family calls me.}Alya, gia đình hay gọi tôi thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:15.63,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah? How about you give me \Npermission to call you Alya, then?}Vậy à? Thế thì cho tớ gọi cậu là Alya đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:18.22,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Huh? What's in it for you, though?}Hả? Trả ơn chỗ nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:21.24,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{You're our class's idol, \Nthe apple of everyone's eye.}Cậu là thần tượng của cả lớp và \Nchỉ riêng tớ được gọi tên.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:24.48,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{And I get the glory of being \Nthe only guy who calls you by your nickname!}Đó là vinh dự của tớ rồi còn gì!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.94,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Are you okay in the head?}Cậu bị ngốc à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.52,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Thank you for this glorious gift!}Cảm ơn vì món quà!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:28.74,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Gross!}Kinh tởm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.78,flashback,BOY4,0,0,0,,{E-Excuse me. Kujo-san?}X-Xin lỗi, Kujo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.16,flashback,BOY4,0,0,0,,{Would you please dance with me?}Cậu có thể nhảy với tớ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.76,flashback,BOY5,0,0,0,,{Hey! Who said you could go first?!}Này! Ai cho cậu mời trước?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:39.47,flashback,BOY5,0,0,0,,{Alisa-san! I've been \Ninterested in you for a while now!}Alisa! Tớ đã thích cậu từ lâu rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.08,flashback,BOY5,0,0,0,,{Please dance with me!}Hãy nhảy với tớ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.71,flashback,BOY6,0,0,0,,{Dude, you practically asked her out! No fair!}Này, đây không phải lúc tỏ tình! Đừng có gian manh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:46.80,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry. I can't dance.}Xin lỗi, tôi không nhảy được...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:50.34,flashback,BOY5,0,0,0,,{Come on! All you gotta do \Nis move with the music.}Không sao! Cậu chỉ cần di chuyển theo nhạc thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:53.26,flashback,BOY6,0,0,0,,{Yeah, you'll be fine! \NI can't really dance either!}Phải đó! Tớ cũng có biết nhảy đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:55.12,flashback,BOY6,0,0,0,,{Just go with the vibes!}Chỉ cần nhảy theo giai điệu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.85,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Okay, you all need to calm down.}Các cậu bình tĩnh lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:01.05,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Sorry, boys, she's taken.}Xin lỗi nhé, anh đây húp trước rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:05.36,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Let's go, Alya.}Đi thôi Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:07.43,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{H-Hey!}N-Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:17.87,flashback italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,Trái tim mình... kêu to quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:22.25,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Oh, remember what you said?}Phải rồi, lúc nãy cậu đã nói gì nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:26.00,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{You used to practice ballet, \Nso you can pick up folk dancing easily, right?}Từng học ba lê, cỡ này 1 phút là xong nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.38,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Y-Yeah?}À ừ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:30.68,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Let's see what you've got, then,}Vậy thì thử xem có thật không.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.26,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Princess.}Công chúa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:35.39,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{You're on!}Được thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:48.65,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Morning, Alya.}Chào buổi sáng Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:55.54,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Hey, what's up? You're looking \Nat me like I'm human garbage.}Gì nữa? Sao nhìn tớ như bãi rác thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:56.46,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,{You waste of space.}Đồ rác rưởi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:58.03,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Sharp-tongued, much?!}Sao ác mồm vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:05.04,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnGeorgia\c&H353B44&\an9\3c&HF8F9FA&}{Best Attraction Award\NClass Event Category\NClass 3-B}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:03.54,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}{Just when I'd thought you were so cool last night.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:07.79,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{I get it now.}Ra là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:11.80,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{That's what made you fall for him, huh? \NWhat a lovely story!}Và em đã thích cậu ấy nhỉ? Tuyệt vời.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:15.32,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Again, it's not like that. \NWere you even listening to me?}Không phải. Nãy giờ chị có nghe em không thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.54,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{What?}Nghe gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:20.06,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{That clearly sounded like \Nthe start of a beautiful love story.}Thì nghe về câu chuyện tình của em.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:24.56,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Stop being weird about it. \NI told you, we're friends.}Đừng có nói kiểu đó. Bọn em là bạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:29.56,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Ah, yes, from friends to lovers. \NThe classic progression.}Ừm ừm, từ bạn bè thành người tình. \NMotip thường thấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:32.82,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Sa-kun and I were like that, too.}Sa-kun và chị cũng thế nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.17,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Weren't we?}Nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:39.08,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{All that aside, you get it now.}Mà cũng phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:43.33,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I know how capable he is, and I trust him.}Em thừa nhận năng lực và tin tưởng vào cậu ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:46.98,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Boys who get things done \Nwhen it counts really do shine, huh?}Những chàng trai hoàn thành công việc\Nmỗi khi cần đúng là luôn toả sáng nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:49.30,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Sa-kun was the same.}Sa-kun cũng vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:53.08,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Back when he saved me \Nfrom the dog attack, he was so...}Hồi xưa cậu ấy đã cứu chị khi bị chó tấn công...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:55.22,Default,ASHA,0,0,0,,{Can you go brag about \Nyour love life somewhere else?}Nếu khoe khoang về tình yêu thì mời chị ra khỏi phòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:58.36,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Come on, Alya-chan! You big meanie!}Thôi nào! Em lạnh lùng quá đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.97,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H292D31&\3c&HDFE7E4&\frx8\fry346\frz8.023\pos(320.001,270)}{Student Council Office}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:03.97,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Excuse me.}Xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:05.84,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{Hey there, Kuze.}A, Kuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:08.98,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{Thanks for coming to help.}Cảm ơn vì đã đến giúp đỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:12.62,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Oh, I'm just here to cover for Yuki.}À không, em chỉ đến đây phụ Yuki thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:15.61,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{My, so you're Kuze-kun?}Em là Kuze nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:18.99,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{I'm Mariya Mikhailovna Kujo.}Chị là Mariya Mikhailovna Kujo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:22.27,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Alya-chan's big sis \Nand student council secretary.}Chị gái của Alya, thư kí hội học sinh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:23.87,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Nice to meet you.}Rất vui được gặp em.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.29,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Hello.}Chào chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.64,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Alya's been a great friend to me.}Alya luôn quan tâm đến em.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:31.38,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{I heard you needed someone \Nto go shopping with you, Kujo-senpai.}Nghe nói hôm nay chị Kujo cần người phụ đi mua sắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.52,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Please, call me Masha.}Gọi chị là Masha đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:38.88,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Any friend of Alya-chan's \Nis a friend to me, too.}Bạn của Alya thì là bạn chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:42.51,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Oh... Masha-san, then.}Vậy thì chị Masha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:49.82,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Very good. Again, \Nit's a pleasure to meet... you?}Tốt. Rất vui được gặp... em?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:53.15,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Wh-What's wrong?}S-Sao vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:56.53,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Kuze-kun, what's your given name?}Kuze, họ của em là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:19:02.03,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Huh? It's Masachika, \Nmeaning "together with diplomacy."}Là Masachika, gần nghĩa với "Cùng nhau hoà hợp".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:05.37,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Masa... chika?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:10.19,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{What's wrong? Is there something behind Kuze?}Sao thế? Phía sau Kuze có vong theo hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:14.30,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Prez, shouldn't you ask if there's \Nsomething on my face first?}Anh đừng nói câu đó với \Nkhuôn mặt bình thản được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.80,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{Nice comeback!}Trả treo ghê đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:20.55,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Oh, sorry about that.}Xin lỗi em.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:25.38,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{I was just so happy to meet Alya-chan's friend.}Chỉ là vui khi gặp bạn của Alya thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:26.56,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Right...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.93,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}{Right, shall we get going?}Chúng ta đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:34.19,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Uh, what was that?}Vừa rồi là gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:40.20,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Oh, right, sorry. I said, "Shall we get going?"}Xin lỗi, chị nói "Đi thôi nhỉ"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:42.15,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Oh, sure.}À vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:44.64,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{See you later, President.}Vậy bọn em đi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.14,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,{Yeah, take care of it.}Ừ, cẩn thận đường xá.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:50.98,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{How about this aromatic here?}Mùi này thì sao nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.83,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{I don't think that's \Na good idea for the office.}Em nghĩ phòng hội học sinh\N không nên dùng dầu thơm đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:55.96,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{That belongs more in your own room.}Cái đó chị nên dùng ở phòng riêng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.21,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Gosh!}Á!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:00.92,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Look at this kitty plushie!}Nhìn con mèo này xem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:03.22,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{It looks just like Alya-chan!}Y như Alya luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:05.22,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{I've got it!}Phải rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:10.37,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{How about getting a plushi\e that \Nresembles each student council officer?}Mua thú nhồi bông theo từng \Nthành viên hội học sinh thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:12.23,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Are you trying to build a theme park?}Chị tính mở công viên à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:18.00,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{The girls may like it, but I bet it'll \Nmake the prez uncomfortable as hell.}Con gái thì em không nói nhưng hội trưởng thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:19.87,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{For him,}Hội trưởng,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:22.48,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{we'll get this bespectacled lion over here.}sẽ là con sư tử đeo kính này.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:23.65,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Listen, seriously...}Này... em đã nói...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:25.24,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Wait, that does look like him!}Giống thật đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:27.47,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{We'll get this, then.}Chúng ta sẽ lấy nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:31.25,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Sure, it looks like him, \Nbut I don't think plushies are gonna fly.}Đúng là giống thật nhưng không được đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:32.88,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{What...}Gì chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:35.32,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Right back at you.}Em cũng muốn nói câu đó đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:38.25,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Fine.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:42.26,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{But I'll get this kitty for myself. It's cute.}Nhưng chị sẽ mua con mèo này cho mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:44.72,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Better not get it on the same receipt.}Đừng tính tiền chung nhé...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:47.31,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Alya'll get mad at you. She's the treasurer.}Alya sẽ giận lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:54.73,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Help. She's way too eccentric.}Chị ấy quá ngây ngô...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:57.00,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Is she always like this?}Lúc nào cũng thế này à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:01.77,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{If she is, then Alya must've \Ngone through a lot.}Nếu vậy thì Alya hẳn phải khổ tâm lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:06.03,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{This is the place, Kuze-kun.}Chỗ này nè Kuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:09.48,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Oh, okay. I'll hold that for you.}À vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:11.74,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn em.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:14.75,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Take care of Alya-nyan for me.}Vậy thì chăm sóc Alyanyan cho chị nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:15.92,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{A...}A...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:18.32,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Alya-nyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.73,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{My, you two look great together.}Hai em hợp nhau lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:23.82,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{I have doubts about your tastes.}Chị nghĩ sao mà bảo hợp...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:25.38,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Say cheese.}Cười lên nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.90,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Oh, no you don't.}Không đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:29.42,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Come on, what's the big deal?}Có sao đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.42,0:21:31.78,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Aren't we here to pick up tea?}Thôi nào, chúng ta đi mua trà đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:34.08,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Ugh, fine.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:37.70,Default,TEAMANS,0,0,0,,{Here.}Đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:39.30,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:41.90,Default,TEAMANS,0,0,0,,{These leaves are first flush, \Nso they have a slight bitterness.}Đây là lá non nên có dư vị đắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:43.27,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Say, Kuze-kun.}Nè Kuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:45.65,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{What do you think?}Em nghĩ sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:48.80,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Uh, I'm not really an expert in red teas.}Em không rành về hồng trà lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.03,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{No?}Không?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:57.29,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Yuki could probably chime in. \NThat mother of ours has taught her a lot.}Nếu là Yuki thì hẳn phải biết rõ \Nvì được bà ta chỉ dạy rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:21:59.17,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{But I...}Còn mình thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:01.35,flashback,KYOTARO,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, Masachika.}Xin lỗi nhé Masachika.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:06.10,flashback,KYOTARO,0,0,0,,{Your mother and I have\Ndecided to live separately.}Ba và mẹ sẽ ly hôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:08.98,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:14.43,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Then I'll follow... \NI'll choose to go with you, Dad.}Vậy con sẽ... đi cùng ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.07,0:22:19.94,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, Nii-sama.}Em xin lỗi anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.91,0:22:23.94,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,{I'm going to stay here.}Em sẽ ở lại đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:26.94,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Kuze-kun?}Kuze?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.51,0:22:29.86,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Is something wrong?}Có chuyện gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.86,0:22:32.37,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{N-No, it's nothing.}Không ạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.31,0:22:36.25,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{You look terribly pained.}Trông em đau khổ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:43.64,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{It's okay.}Không sao cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:45.74,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{There, there.}Ngoan ngoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.29,0:22:48.84,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{What is this feeling?}Cảm giác này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:53.36,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{It's so familiar... and so relaxing.}Thật hoài niệm... và thoải mái...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:58.27,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Ow! Hot!}Nóng!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.72,0:22:59.48,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Oh?}Ớ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:02.27,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{M-Masha-san! The tea's touching my back!}T-Trà! Ly trà của chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:03.02,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Oh, dear.}Ấy chết...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.02,0:23:06.37,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Ow!}Á!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:08.26,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,{Oh, dear!}Nóng!
